A '''protestor''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Edward Tudor Pole]] and only appears in &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]].&quot; He spreads dissent against the rule of King [[Joffrey Baratheon]] and [[House Lannister]].
